{"tid":568743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（樓價gogogo) 三分一已婚者與伴侶分居","createTime":"2018-02-22T05:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T09:45:34.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"062b476dc90921994e7ee183c86c3d9df14dc87a","tid":568743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"自立艱難，青年仍普遍與父母同住，比例達94%，10年間水平相約。此外，雖然統計處指青年居住情況與其婚姻狀況有很大關係，逾半數已婚青年與配偶子女同住，但有逾5,100名（32.5%）已婚青年並無與另一半同住，而要與父母同住；連同272名獨居已婚青年，平均每3個已婚青年就有1個不與配偶同住。另有13.2%已婚青年婚後和配偶與父母同居。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/133241_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F133241_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ed3b5348&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8469a1e5188c570375626dcd266948509339a6c","tid":568743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090e8603dc66ff4b35b3c6ceb6bbd1173ac523be","tid":568743,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"假結婚囉<br />\n<br />\n否則邊會20年都仲可以每日150人爆QUOTA, 有乜可能？"},{"pid":"56bd3890a91e8758f39b18cd17b0a317ffbfd87c","tid":568743,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"20年過去, 所謂「家庭團聚」長團長有, 團極唔完, 永續團聚<br />\n<br />\n今時今日都仲可以每日150人爆晒QUOTA<br />\n<br />\n邊撚有咁多家庭要團呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔係假結婚, 鬼信？<br />\n<br />\n紅底01有無做過假結婚報導？"},{"pid":"ab1fb07dc9a2db938a568097ccf8f4dbd895a7c5","tid":568743,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"090e8603dc66ff4b35b3c6ceb6bbd1173ac523be","tid":568743,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:53:43.000Z","msg":"假結婚囉<br />\n<br />\n否則邊會20年都仲可以每日150人爆QUOTA, 有乜可能？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:59:06.000Z","msg":"係